pull.body:
Requires ACK from @jgarzik.

This file was also modified on 2016-03-29 by @jonasschnelli, but was ACKed by him in PR #8676 for 2229ffa5e2b8e38cd962c02e2fc892e0c925675b before it was taken out and split off into this PR.

events.message: [copyright] add MIT License copyright header to zmq_sub.py

events.body:
According to @jgarzik, the work that added zmq_sub.py in e6a14b64d665eb1fafd03a6bbc8d14597ce1c83c is attributable to @jmcorgan.

@jmcorgan, would you be able to ACK that a MIT License header is appropriate here? Much thanks!
